# TripWeaver UI Test Summary

This document provides a summary of all UI tests created for the TripWeaver application.

## Test Files Created

### 1. Configuration and Setup
- `setup.ts` - Test utilities and helper functions
- `config.ts` - Test constants, selectors, and configuration
- `testSuite.ts` - Test suite runner
- `jest.config.js` - Jest configuration for UI tests

### 2. Screen Tests
- `screens/LoginScreen.test.tsx` - Authentication flow tests
- `screens/HomeScreen.test.tsx` - Trip listing and management tests
- `screens/CreateTripScreen.test.tsx` - Trip creation tests
- `screens/ItineraryScreen.test.tsx` - Itinerary and destination management tests
- `screens/BudgetScreen.test.tsx` - Budget tracking and expense management tests
- `screens/MapScreen.test.tsx` - Map visualization tests
- `screens/ProfileScreen.test.tsx` - User profile and settings tests
- `screens/NotificationsScreen.test.tsx` - Notification system tests

### 3. Navigation Tests
- `navigation/AppNavigator.test.tsx` - App navigation flow tests

### 4. Integration Tests
- `integration/CrossScreenIntegration.test.tsx` - Cross-screen workflow tests

