## Mocking Strategy

- Redux state mocked with `jest.mock('react-redux')`
- API calls mocked with `jest.mock()` for service modules
- Navigation mocked with `@react-navigation/native` mocks
- Native modules mocked through Jest setup
- Third-party libraries mocked as needed

